## GitOps Integration

### ArgoCD

ArgoCD applications are defined in `deploy/argocd/{{ project_slug }}/`:

```bash
# Apply ArgoCD applications
kubectl apply -f deploy/argocd/{{ project_slug }}/

# Sync applications
argocd app sync {{ project_name }}
argocd app sync {{ project_name }}-staging
argocd app sync {{ project_name }}-prod
```

### Flux

Flux can be used for GitOps automation:

```bash
# Generate Flux manifests
flux generate kustomization {{ project_name }} \
    --source=GitRepository/{{ project_name }} \
    --path="./deploy/apps/{{ project_slug }}/overlays/dev"

# Sync Flux resources
flux reconcile kustomization {{ project_name }}
```

## OCI Registry

### Publishing Charts

Helm charts can be published to OCI registry:

```bash
# Package chart
helm package deploy/charts/{{ project_slug }}/

# Push to OCI registry
helm push {{ project_name }}-{{ chart_version }}.tgz oci://{{ oci_registry }}/{{ project_name }}

# Install from OCI registry
helm install {{ project_name }} oci://{{ oci_registry }}/{{ project_name }} \
    --version {{ chart_version }}
```

### OCI Registry Configuration

Configure OCI registry in values:

```yaml
oci:
  registry: "ghcr.io/myorg"
  enabled: true
  chart:
    repository: "{{ oci_registry }}/{{ project_name }}"
```

