## Testing

### Helm Unit Testing

The boilerplate includes comprehensive Helm unit testing using the `helm-unittest` plugin. Tests are located in `deploy/charts/{{ project_slug }}/tests/` and cover all major chart components.

#### Test Structure

```
deploy/charts/{{ project_slug }}/tests/
├── deployment_test.yaml      # Deployment resource tests
├── service_test.yaml         # Service resource tests
├── ingress_test.yaml         # Ingress resource tests
├── configmap_test.yaml       # ConfigMap resource tests
├── secret_test.yaml          # Secret resource tests
├── hpa_test.yaml             # HPA resource tests
├── serviceaccount_test.yaml  # ServiceAccount resource tests
└── _helpers_test.yaml        # Template helper tests
```

#### Running Tests

```bash
# Run all Helm unit tests
just helm-unittest

# Run tests with verbose output
just helm-unittest-verbose

